spec_data.Name: python2-ludolph-zabbix
spec_data.Description:
Ludolph: Zabbix API plugin.

Plugin for Ludolph Monitoring Jabber Bot support Zabbix monitoring system.
Python 2 module with Ludolph: Zabbix API plugin. Use the python3-ludolph and\
python3-ludolph-zabbix package to get the actual application and service.
